text: Georgy Zakyrich (, born 1884, date of death unknown) was a Russian fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
